sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Session Log
  participant E as Evidence Selector
  participant X as Extractor
  participant L as Candidate Ledger
  participant G as Governance
  participant M as Memory Store

  S->>E: Select events that can be used as evidence
  E->>X: Provide user rules, tool observations, and verification results
  X-->>L: Write pending candidates
  L->>G: Trigger governance check
  G-->>L: Update status and reason
  G->>M: Only approved items go to long-term storage
